awards.title: B+ Scholarship
awards.summary: Scholarships awarded to incoming freshmen and continuing students who complete a rigorous high school curriculum with a minimum overall GPA of 3.0 at a Hawai'i public school.

awards.title: Manoa Academic Merit Scholarship
awards.summary: Scholarship is an automatic $4,000 scholarship per year for four years of undergraduate study for first-time degree seeking students. Students must have a 3.5 GPA, 1200 SAT or 23 ACT upon the time of application to UH Manoa.

awards.title: Dean's List
awards.summary: Undergraduate students are awarded the Dean's List distinction when they have earned a semester GPA of 3.5 or higher and were enrolled in 12 or more credits for a grade.
